responseText: I admit some concern. See, goblins aren't much brighter than my little nephew Timmy; He's not too smart, you understand. But if they've hit on a strategy, well, I'd just like to make sure we stay ahead of them is all. Go take a good look at those crates they drug up to the walls, there's nothing good in those, I'd wager.
name: SQ_Lionhold_0001_GoblinsAttack_Coyle_5_Response
